    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>I am a Computer Engineering student at Georgia Tech with hands-on experience in firmware, embedded systems, and PCB design through the Georgia Tech Solar Racing Team. I am seeking a Summer 2026 internship to apply my technical skills and collaborative mindset to real-world engineering challenges.</p>
