  <section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>

    <div class="project">
      <h3>GT Solar Racing MC2 Rev7</h3>
      <p>Led redesign of the motor controller board, migrating from TI Tiva to STM32 MCU, integrating CAN-based magnetometers, and reworking schematic, PCB layout, and firmware for improved noise immunity and communication.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h3>Asteroid Destroyer Game (ARM MBED)</h3>
      <p>Programmed a classic arcade game in C on an ARM MBED microcontroller with LCD output, including real-time gameplay logic, collision detection, scoring, and performance optimization.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h3>RFID Door Lock</h3>
      <p>Designed an RFID-enabled door lock using Arduino, combining C++ firmware with supporting circuits for secure authentication and hardware control.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="project">
      <h3>Custom Desktop Build</h3>
      <p>Built a desktop computer from scratch, gaining practical knowledge of hardware integration and system-level component interaction.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

